latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The wait is Over! All the episodes of  Myntra Fashion Superstar, Season 3 are almost here !  With the most coveted panel of judges led by the shaper of the Fashion Industry in India, @manishmalhotra05 to the MVPs of social media, @kushakapila, @aashnashroff, @ankushbahuguna, and @santu.misra, this season is not to be missed. 12 handpicked social media veterans battle for the title of India's Next Big Fashion Influencer in this super-woke 8-part fashion reality series.
Tune in from tomorrow the 18th of November on @Myntra and @voot to find out who bags the title this year!

#MFSIwearMyStory, #MyntraFashionSuperstar, #MyntraStudioOriginals #myntrastudio

It's been 2 days since the launch of #MyntraFashionSuperstar season 3 and it still seems unreal! I had the best time being a part of it. Here’s a glimpse of what’s coming next on the show! You don’t wanna miss it. Tune in to watch it now only on @Myntra studio or @Voot! Link in bio!
#MFSIWearMyStory #MyntraStudioOriginals #MyntraStudio #ad

Myntra Fashion Superstar, Season 3 is back! And this time, the game is next level. With the most coveted panel of judges led by the shaper of the Fashion Industry in India, @manishmalhotra05 to the MVPs of social media, @kushakapila, @aashnashroff, @ankushbahuguna, and @santu.misra, this season is not to be missed. 12 handpicked social media veterans battle for the title of India's Next Big Fashion Influencer in this super-woke 8-part fashion reality series.

Tune in from the 11th of November on @Myntra and @voot to find out who bags the title this year!
